headline: Chipotle flexes its new high-protein menu
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (CMG) is flexing some muscle as it is now offering its first-ever high-protein menu, with its new Double High Protein Bowl offering as much as 81 grams of protein. Yahoo Finance senior reporter Brooke DiPalma examines the fast-casual chain's latest strategy to capture consumer attention.
